(2000000842,'Hail, Gezhe!  Seventeen more orders have been placed in the Hara\'samid Sector.  The markets of heavy veldarite have all but collapsed, as you predicted.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
